Package: psmsl.org
Title: Permanent Service for Mean Sea Level (PSMSL) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the PSMSL tide gauge data. Lists all
    RLR stations worldwide and fetches annual mean sea level records.
    Includes LLM context injection via psmsl_context().
